causal_map:
Time-domain signal → Fourier transform; 
Fourier transform → Frequency-domain representation; 
Frequency-domain representation → Kernel H(s); 
Kernel H(s) → Filtered signal in frequency domain; 
Filtered signal in frequency domain → Inverse Fourier transform → Time-domain filtered signal; 
Time-domain filtered signal → Filtering method (time-invariant vs. time-varying) → H(s) or H(t, s)
